snippet.title: Live Coding: Custom Minecraft server and plugin setup (Day 0)
snippet.description: Support the stream: https://streamlabs.com/devdungeon In this stream we will set up a custom Minecraft server from scratch for DevDungeon. We will cover the basics of setting up a vanilla server, then a custom one with plugins. We'll look in to how to find plugins and create your own. If we have enough time we will look at how to integrate with Discord, databases, and websites.
